# 🏀 Kobe Bryant — Tribute Page

**Intern:** Utkarsh  
**Task:** Level 2 — Task 2  
**File:** `Tribute_page.html`

## 📌 Overview
A visually rich tribute page dedicated to Kobe Bryant — basketball legend, Olympic champion, and Academy Award winner. Built with Lakers purple and gold theme.

## 🎯 Features
- ✅ Hero section with name, dates, and quote
- ✅ Career statistics grid
- ✅ Full biography section
- ✅ Career timeline — 10 key moments
- ✅ Honours and achievements cards
- ✅ SVG scoring chart across career seasons
- ✅ Mamba Mentality quote section
- ✅ Gianna Bryant tribute section
- ✅ Fully responsive design

## 🖥️ Tech Stack
| Technology | Usage |
|------------|-------|
| HTML5 | Semantic structure |
| CSS3 | Custom properties, grid, flexbox |
| SVG | Inline chart and decorative elements |

## 🚀 How to Run
Open `Tribute_page.html` in any browser. Internet needed for Google Fonts.

